{
  "stem": "11916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a student in my father's workshop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But coincidentally, he was a soldier also in the jail, where my father was staying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, when nobody see it, he come and gave us messages from father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was really risking his own life to do this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About five days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I was like to point out, which is a very hard thing for all the women endure, which was happening.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because before, we was taken to the barracks-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they wanted everything you have in gold-- everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they take you to one place, and they said, you still have gold, and you did not give it to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was about-- man in one room and a woman in the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] First they looked through mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't find anything in her, because we wouldn't do things like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I have to go through with this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a very torturous things to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I never forgot my mother screaming and pain when it was happen with me, because I was roughly, roughly treated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it's happened with most of the young girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they could, they'd destroy you, or half destroy you, so you never be the same woman again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because even if you were hurt, there was no doctor, there was no help.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they was very disappointed if they don't find this gold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But before we went into this, we have some gold in our necklace, some ring and things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We gave them-- this to them, but this wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they was really known by the Hungarian government and everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
